akka.actor.testkit.typed

Class Effect

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.actor.testkit.typed.Effect
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Effect.MessageAdapter, Effect.NoEffects, Effect.ReceiveTimeoutCancelled, Effect.ReceiveTimeoutSet, Effect.Scheduled, Effect.Spawned, Effect.SpawnedAdapter, Effect.SpawnedAnonymous, Effect.SpawnedAnonymousAdapter, Effect.Stopped, Effect.Unwatched, Effect.Watched

    public abstract class Effect
extends java.lang.Object
    All tracked effects for the BehaviorTestKit and BehaviorTestKit must extend this type.

    Factories/types for effects are available through Effects and Effects

    Not for user extension
